## SERP ANALYSIS

### Competitor Summary

- **Word Count Range:** 800–2,500 words (avg: ~1,400). Most are image-heavy gallery posts with thin editorial text. Few offer structured design categorisation.
- **Visual Patterns:** 15–50 images standard; Instagram embeds common. Scratch Magazine ran 50 Instagram embeds with minimal copy. ThePinkIssue used 40 designs with short blurbs. Heavier editorial pages (Who What Wear, Marie Claire) run 600–1,000 words of copy + 8–15 images.
- **Common H2 Topics Across Competitors:**
